{"id":1265318766,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 month, 3 weeks","timestamp":1716425265,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"78 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1265318766/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"45 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        int longest = 0;\n\n        HashMap<Character, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();\n\n        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {\n            if (!map.containsKey(s.charAt(i))) {\n                map.put(s.charAt(i), i);\n                longest = Math.max(longest, map.size());\n            } else {\n                i = map.get(s.charAt(i));\n                map.clear();\n            }\n        }\n\n        return longest;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
